    "long_instructions": "## Video Game Developer - Level 2: One-Shot Prompting\r\n\r\nPractice one-shot prompting through the career of a video game developer by adding a single example to help guide the AI’s dialogue.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a prompt like the one below, or write a similar one that includes an example of a hero-villain exchange.\r\n\r\n>Here’s an example: “Hero: You can’t stop me. Villain: We’ll see about that.” Now create a dialogue between a hero and villain where the villain reveals their ultimate plan.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, noticing how the AI uses the example to shape tone, style, or plot.",
